cover_flow - demo application. Shows animated DVD covers on screen.

Parameters:
 -width val    render width (default 640)
 -height val   render height (default 480)
 -samples val  number of samples for AA (default 0)
 -steps val    animation speed (default 16)
 -frames val   number of frames to render (default 0 = no limit)
 -etc1         use pkm textures instead of tga (default tga)

Example:
  cover_flow -width 1024 -height 768 -steps 150 -frames 2000

Keyboard control:
  ESC          quit
  Left/Right   select image
  A/G/R        enable/disable auto-run (enabled by default)
  ,/keypad -   rotate left
  ./keypad +   rotate right
  space        reset rotation